{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878012", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "## 诊断摘要"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878106", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**错误码 5400103 (MSERR_EXT_API9_IO)** — AVPlayer IO 错误"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878188", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "### 三个可能的根因（按可能性排序）："}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878274", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "1. **资源管理不当（高置信度）**：多段音频切换时，fdSrc 的文件描述符被提前关闭，或 reset() 后未等待 idle 状态就设置新 url，导致数据源初始化 IO 失败。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878361", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "2. **长时间运行资源压力（中置信度）**：频繁的 prepare/reset 循环导致底层 Pipeline 资源泄漏，累积后触发间歇性 IO 错误。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878437", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "3. **网络间歇性波动（中置信度）**：如果是网络音频源，长时间播放中偶发的网络抖动会触发 5400103。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878505", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "### 核心修复建议："}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878578", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "- 严格遵循状态机：`stop() → reset() → 等待 idle → 设置 url → prepare() → play()`"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878654", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "- fdSrc 的 FD 在播放期间保持打开，仅在 `release()` 后关闭"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878727", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "- error 回调中先 `reset()` 回到 idle，再重新设置数据源"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T23:16:30.878798", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "- 考虑在多段音频间适当调用 `release()` 彻底释放资源后重建实例"}
